quot;:410}"><font color="#000000">Erfunden von Lennart Falkenberg | Advertorial | Maschinenbauingenieur aus Freiburg</font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:351,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:19,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:410}"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Zuletzt aktualisiert: vor 2 Stunden | Bestseller in: Deutschland, Österreich, Schweiz</span></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659483" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659483" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:400,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:480,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:459}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:400,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:480,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:459}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/5f5b9afe-9676-4e16-9ed6-c7b256299e62/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/1.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:400,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:480,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:459}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496101959" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496101959" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:900,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:959}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:900,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:959}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:900,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:959}"><font color="#000000">Die Mission eines Mannes, Rasenpflege neu zu denken</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659535" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659535" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:408,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:408,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Es war ein Sonntagmorgen im Mai, als Lennart Falkenberg auf seinen Knien vor der Einfahrt saß — mit einem Fugenkratzer in der Hand und Unkraut zwischen jedem Stein.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Seit zwei Stunden arbeitete er sich Fuge für Fuge vor. Der Rücken schmerzte. Die Knie waren taub. Und die Hälfte der Einfahrt war noch nicht geschafft.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><i>„Ich habe mir an dem Tag gesagt: Das kann doch nicht die einzige Lösung sein",</i> erinnert sich Falkenberg. <i>„Millionen Menschen knien jedes Frühjahr auf ihren Einfahrten und kratzen Unkraut von Hand. Oder sie sprühen Chemie — die nach zwei Wochen wieder sinnlos ist."</i></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Er wusste: Es muss etwas geben, das schneller geht, den Rücken schont und ohne Gift auskommt.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:955,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1014}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Da war die Idee.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1363,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1422}"><font color="#000000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1363,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1422}"></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1363,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1422}"><font color="#000000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1363,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1422}"></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1363,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1422}"><font color="#000000" bis_size="{&q