ter-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1373,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:22,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1432}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/99a8712d-4efb-406b-ba9e-a4123cd0db75/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/ChatGPT%20Image%2020.%20Apr.%202026,%2015_57_29.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1536" height="1024" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1536" natural-height="1024" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:397,&quot;y&quot;:1396,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:686,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1455}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496146943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496146943" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><font color="#000000">Warum herkömmliche Methoden scheitern</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659468" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659468" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Jeder Gartenbesitzer kennt das Problem: Unkraut in Fugen, Moos zwischen Pflastersteinen, Gras das aus jeder Ritze wächst. Und die üblichen Lösungen sind alle unbefriedigend:</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><strong>Per Hand kratzen?</strong> Stundenlange Arbeit auf den Knien. Am nächsten Wochenende wächst alles nach.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><strong>Unkrautbrenner? </strong>Gefährlich in der Nähe von Holzzäunen und trockenen Pflanzen. Und das Unkraut kommt trotzdem wieder.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><strong>Chemisches Unkrautmittel?</strong> Belastet den Boden, ist in vielen Gemeinden verboten und löst das Problem nur kurzzeitig.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><strong>Normaler Fadentrimmer?</strong> Der Faden reißt bei Steinkontakt sofort. Und Moos in Fugen bekommt man damit gar nicht raus.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Genau hier setzt ProfiTrim an.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693052133" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1776693052133" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1373,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:22,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1432}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1373,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:22,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1432}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/068cacbd-3744-42f4-89ac-c7ca247dccab/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Untitled%20design%20_7_%20_1_.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1500" height="789" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1500" natural-height="789" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:397,&quot;y&quot;:1396,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:686,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1455}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693126143" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1776693126143" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><font color="#000000">Die Geburtsstunde von ProfiTrim – aus Frust entstanden, für die Praxis entwickelt</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693135287" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1776693135287" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Lennart Falkenberg ist Maschinenbauingenieur mit über 15 Jahren Erfahrung. Er fragte sich: Was, wenn man den Plastikfaden am Trimmer durch etwas ersetzt, das Stein aushält?</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><strong>Die Antwort:</strong> Ein Trimmer aus gehärtetem Edelstahl mit 0,5 mm Federstahldraht. Speziell geknotete Drahtbündel, die auch bei Steinkontakt nicht brechen, nicht ausfransen und nicht nachlassen.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Kein neues Gerät. Nur ein Aufsatz — der aus deinem vorhandenen Rasentrimmer ein Unkraut-Entfernungssystem macht.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Aufstecken. Einschalten. Fertig.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659464" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659464" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/8ff4db6a-af04-4bd8-a2c3-396f2ee880cd/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/2.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693272365" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1776693272365" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1426,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1485}"><font color="#000000">Vom Prototyp zum Bestseller</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693279163" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1776693279163" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:720,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Falkenberg baute den ersten Prototyp in seiner Werkstatt im Schwarzwald. Er testete ihn auf seiner eigenen Einfahrt, auf Gehwegen, zwischen Terrassenplatten. Dann bei Nachbarn. Dann bei Gartenbaubetrieben.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Das Feedback war immer dasselbe: <i>„Warum gibt es das nicht schon längst?"</i></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Er nahm das Konzept zu Herstellern. Die Reaktion? Zurückhaltung. Ein Aufsatz, der nicht verschleißt und keine Nachfüll-Spulen braucht — das passte nicht ins Geschäftsmodell.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Also ging Falkenberg seinen eigenen Weg.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Das Ergebnis: ProfiTrim — der unzerstörbare Trimmer, der Unkraut, Moos und Schmutz aus jeder Fuge entfernt.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1505,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1564}">Heute ein <strong>Bestseller </strong>in Deutschland, Österreich und der Schweiz. Über 20.000 zufriedene Kunden.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659432" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659432" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2245,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:533,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2304}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2245,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:533,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2304}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/14d284a4-4feb-4cef-bfec-531f6c8c5402/Untitleddesign3-ezgif.com-optimize.gif" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="600" natural-height="316" width="600" height="316" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2245,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:533,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2304}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496247194" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496247194" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2809,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2868}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2809,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2868}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2809,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2868}"><font color="#000000">Warum es funktioniert – Die Technik erklärt</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659396" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659396" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:240,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:240,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">Herkömmliche Fadentrimmer sind für Gras gemacht — nicht für Fugen. Bei Steinkontakt reißt der Faden, die Spule ist leer, und Moos bleibt sitzen.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">ProfiTrim funktioniert komplett anders:</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🔧 Edelstahl-Bürstenkopf — 0,5 mm Federstahldraht statt Plastikfaden. Reißt nicht, bricht nicht, franst nicht aus.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🔗 Geknotete Drahtbündel — Perfekte Balance, weniger Vibrationen, ermüdungsfreies Arbeiten auch bei längeren Einsätzen.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🔒 Zahnverriegelung — Drähte bleiben auch bei intensivster Nutzung fest. Kein Verrutschen, keine Unwucht.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🔄 Universell kompatibel — Passt auf 99 % aller handelsüblichen Rasentrimmer: Stihl, Gardena, Bosch, Makita, Einhell und mehr.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🪨 Steinresistent — Arbeitet stabil auch auf Pflaster, Kies, unebenen Flächen. Kein Schaden am Aufsatz bei Kontakt.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2853,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2912}">🌿 Ohne Chemie — Entfernt Unkraut mechanisch. Keine Giftstoffe, kein Grundwasser-Problem, keine Verbote.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776693254089" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1776693254089" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/fbd39e65-1fba-4ac3-af5c-9a83c95363f7/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Untitled%20design%20_6_.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1520" natural-height="800" width="1520" height="800" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3113,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3172}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496308373" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" dat